{"tid":2343732,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港增逾60確診再添2死 曾訪2舞廳翁病逝 爆疫聯院首患者亡","createTime":"2020-12-28T07:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T07:03:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fe43a4b9884fefc5347a653f394315b16f6345c4","tid":2343732,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"有長期病患的73歲男病人，居於長沙灣李鄭屋邨孝廉樓，屬於歌舞群組患者，由11月24日開始發病。患者確診後入住明愛醫院，其後病情持續惡化，延至今晨2時38分離世。患者潛伏期曾到過旺角金儷星跳舞，也去過全港最大「疫邨」彩雲邨的彩龍皇宮大酒樓，是該處首名患者。現時歌舞群組累計至少12死。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201228/QN7EJ6FRHNHSPAQY435EDOMQGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201228%2FQN7EJ6FRHNHSPAQY435EDOMQGY%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjdwKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=b5331428\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201228%2FQN7EJ6FRHNHSPAQY435EDOMQGY%2F&h=6645709d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201228/QN7EJ6FRHNHSPAQY435EDOMQGY/</a>"}]}